attributes.review: This app is quite disappointing. i was so looking forward for using this app to support my king, daddy trump, but as soon as i downloaded it, it called me a stupid ugly b*tch and completely wiped my phone! at first i thought of it as a mistake, cause daddy trump would never allow something so vile to come from his app, but then, after about a week, the app jumped out of my phone AND KILLED MY FAMILY!!! so incredibly disappointed!! as if that wasn’t bad enough, after it killed my family, it burned my whole house down and ran off screaming “nazi party 2020” until it was gone. so upset. president trump has lost my vote! don’t download this app!!!!

attributes.review: First of when I looked at all the reviews on this app people kept writing bad reviews, and they were not wrong at all. It took 5 hours to download and when it did it wasn’t even worth it.  When I opened the app it, it was glitching non stop and it wouldn’t even let me touch my screen properly. When I put my mobile phone number in, it said it was going to give me a verification code but it never did so when I tried to put in my email, it kept switching to my moms email. I honestly do not recommend this app because it is a very frustrating, terrible app.
